Package robot_2_0

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Robot
    An interface for classes representing robots moving in a maze, with a limited number of public methods.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Maze
    Maze - a class to contain the data and methods required to represent a maze, and for the maze to be navigable
    MemoryRobot
    A class representing a robot moving randomly through Positions in a Maze, however it will only revisit a previously visited Position if given no other option.
    Position
    Represents positions in a maze and provides methods for reaching adjacent positions.
    RandomRobot
    A class representing a robot moving randomly through Positions in a Maze
    RightHandRuleRobot
    A class representing a robot moving through Positions in a Maze, the robot will always keep a "wall" to the right hand relative to current orientation.
